II. Install Python Environment
  1. Download Anaconda 3: https://www.continuum.io/downloads
  2. Install Anaconda: $ bash Anaconda3-4.3.1-Linux-x86_64.sh

III. Install TensorFlow
  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t_pxnHpRszg&t=158s
  $ conda create -n tensorflow python =3.6
  $ source activate tensorflow
  $ conda install -c conda-forge tensorflow

